race.description: Souths Sports Club F&M Maiden Plate
race.comment: MEADOWBROOK (5) made debut over 1200m here and stalked the speed before dragging the field into the race. Fought on well and was beaten only a length. Better for the experience and over the extra trip will take catching again. REGAL RINA (10) finished alongside MEADOWBROOK on debut, lifting strongly in the run home for a close-up fourth. Has upside and the extra ground a plus. Could well turn the tables. STROMBOLI DELIGHT (9) was tested to a mile before a spell and returns on the back of two trials. Placed only try course and distance. Trip suits fresh and will be running on hard. PENSIERO (6) was safely held fresh over six furlongs but looks a big improver. Has the blinkers added for this. IN SOCIETY (4) wasn't far away fresh over 1400m at Eagle Farm but did cover ground sitting three wide. Good draw here and fitter again can improve sharply.
